name: Datascape Zhi - Zhizhi
text: If this card is in your hand: You can target 1 "Datascape" card you control; you cannot Special Summon monsters for the rest of this turn, except Level/Rank 3 or higher monsters, also send 1 "Datascape" card from your Deck to the GY with a different card type (Monster, Spell, or Trap) from the targeted card, and if you do, Special Summon this card, also during the End Phase of this turn, you can add 1 "Datascape" monster from your GY to your hand, except "Datascape Zhi – Zhizhi". You can only use this effect of "Datascape Zhi - Zhizhi" once per turn.
